videos.headline: Bryant connects with Rodgers for 64-yard gain
videos.description: Kelly Bryant calls an audible and it pays off as Clemson breaks off a 64-yard play.

videos.headline: Bryant runs for 1st Tigers' TD
videos.description: Kelly Bryant jukes out a defender as he goes untouched for a Clemson touchdown.

videos.headline: Higgins Mosses defender, runs for 64-yard TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence connects with Tee Higgins who dives for Clemson's second touchdown.

videos.headline: Clemson ahead of Texas A&M at the half
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence throws for a touchdown and Kelly Bryant runs for one, giving Clemson a 14-3 lead at the half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson ahead of Texas A&M at the half) 2018/9/8 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas A&M backup QB coughs up football to Clemson
videos.description: Nick Starkel checks into the game and is strip-sacked at the Clemson 30-yard line by Justin Foster.

videos.headline: Bryant delivers dart to Overton for Clemson TD
videos.description: Kelly Bryant connects with Diondre Overton down the middle for a 9-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Mond finds Rogers for Texas A&M's 1st TD
videos.description: Kellen Mond rolls out to his left and throws to Kendrick Rogers who hauls it in for a 9-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Clemson's Etienne shows Manziel money hands after short TD
videos.description: Clemson's Travis Etienne takes the pitch to score a 1-yard touchdown and celebrates like Johnny Manziel used to at Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Mond avoids sack, throws 14-yard TD
videos.description: Kellen Mond rolls out to the left and lofts a pass to Quartney Davis for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Texas A&M commits costly fumble into the end zone
videos.description: Kellen Mond connects with Quartney Davis who is stripped by K'Von Wallace resulting in a Texas A&M turnover.

videos.headline: Rogers makes incredible TD catch, but 2-point conversion is no good
videos.description: Kendrick Rogers hauls in a great catch for a 24-yard touchdown, but the potential game-tying two-point conversion fails.

videos.headline: Dabo: 'We found a way to win' against Aggies
videos.description: Dabo Sweeney says  he is proud of Clemson's ability to fight through adversity and pull out the two-point win.

videos.headline: Clemson holds off Texas A&M after late drama
videos.description: A late fumble and a failed two-point conversion cost Texas A&M as Clemson gets three combined touchdowns from Kelly Bryant and Trevor Lawrence.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson holds off Texas A&M after late drama) 2018/9/8 ESHEET SOTFULL
